  "title": "Clinic Assistant (Patient Service & Clinical Support)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>Clinic Assistants support patient service, treatment programme management, and clinical operations under doctor supervision. Responsibilities include coordinating appointments and ensuring treatment frequency follows the doctor-prescribed regimen.</p><p>Clinics are located island-wide, including Central Area medical centres next to MRT stations such as Scotts Medical Centre, Novena Medical Centre, and Raffles Place.<br /><strong>诊所助理（患者服务与临床支持）</strong></p><p><strong>招聘诊所助理，协助患者服务、治疗方案管理及临床日常运作，并在医生监督下工作。</strong></p><p><strong>诊所分布于全岛多个地点，包括靠近地铁站的市中心医疗中心。</strong></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>- Patient reception and appointment coordination</p><p>- Treatment programme scheduling based on doctor instructions</p><p>- Assisting doctors during consultations and treatments</p><p>- Supporting medical and wellness therapies, including post-treatment care</p><p>- Preparing treatment rooms and maintaining clinical hygiene</p><p>- Updating patient records and supporting daily clinic operations</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Minimum GCE O-Level or Polytechnic Diploma</p><p>- Preferably in medical, allied health, biomedical, or hospitality fields</p><p>- Medical clinic experience preferred</p><p>- Willingness to learn and work in a clinical environment<br /></p><p><strong>基本要求：</strong></p><p><strong>- 至少 O 水准或理工学院文凭</strong></p><p><strong>- 医疗、辅助医疗、生物医学或酒店管理相关背景优先</strong></p><p><strong>- 有医疗诊所经验者更佳</strong></p><p><strong>- 愿意学习并适应临床环境</strong></p><p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Application:</strong></a><br />Complete the form before applying:<a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://forms.gle/BANHb1kAYwBY7k6D8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://forms.gle/BANHb1kAYwBY7k6D8</a></p><p>Pay package within the stated range will be commensurate with relevant experienceand educational qualifications.</p><p><br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Please be advised that only shortlisted candidates will benotified.</a></p>",
